{"tid":1093971,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇踢波好勁既人走去打場NBA可以輕易上雙 但打NBA最勁去踢場英超就變咗透明","createTime":"2019-04-06T02:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-06T03:06:42.000Z","uid":92376,"like":3,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"95f4e1332b018284c83595e1c1d8dc054d5ad976","tid":1093971,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T02:59:45.000Z","msg":"我腦內自行來模擬這個事情會發生！！！<br />\n唔駛用小花同牙朗<br />\n我只派出夏薩特去美國打一場NBA 神奇既事情竟然發生<br />\n佢打足四節 有雙雙 28分+10助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成為國際體育新聞既一時佳話<br />\n<br />\n然後心有不甘既NBA決定派出聯盟最強既咖喱同夏登分別去英超同西甲踢一場波諗住為NBA挽回臉子<br />\n點知一個撞到波皮都掂唔到 30分鐘未夠就比哥狗換走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另一個就爭頂當搶籃板 踢踢下玩單擋 最後比人紅撚埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來踢波既球星可以極速適應nba<br />\n相反就唔可以了<br />\n結論 ⚽&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;🏀"},{"pid":"fa3fe90ef5d6039ee57f7b24515f9ed59b5e6334","tid":1093971,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T03:00:42.000Z","msg":"唉你收皮啦，無幽默感就唔好出黎擺"},{"pid":"5cef8642f52927f8724ecd684232f4e15b100c1e","tid":1093971,"uid":34457,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T03:00:51.000Z","msg":"好撚尷尬呀"},{"pid":"2f1e48c15bfa7979f3a4b87de56c3bcd52152329","tid":1093971,"uid":189134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T03:03:00.000Z","msg":"足球員係NBA世界係好撚矮"},{"pid":"35b8827d747101d89cb09db4cdf35f3b2acebf95","tid":1093971,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2f1e48c15bfa7979f3a4b87de56c3bcd52152329","tid":1093971,"uid":189134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T03:03:00.000Z","msg":"足球員係NBA世界係好撚矮"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T03:04:02.000Z","msg":"cp3同艾佛遜都好矮但好知名"},{"pid":"6